1. *Brineš* se da će biti lepo vreme. (You hope that the weather will be nice.)

2. On *brineše* sto se tiče odgovornosti za nastalu štetu. (He was worried about the responsibility for the damage caused.)

3. Oni *brinu* o svojim deci. (They worry about their children.)

4. Gde su moji sunčani naočari, ja *brinem* se da ih nisam izgubila. (I'm worried that I haven't lost my sunglasses.)

5. Nema potrebe da se *brineš* za mene. (There's no need to worry about me.)